narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great course. Great topics and discussions everyday.

This course is wonderful! Professor Adesola is a great person and makes learning the language fun. You will be surprised by how much progress you can make in a single semester while also learning key concepts about Nigerian culture, food, and social life. The course integrates film, theater, and song in a delightful way. The work load is very manageable and Professor Adesola makes every effort to ensure your success!
I would take it! It's an amazing class!!
TAKE THIS COURSE! JUST DO IT!!!!
Take this course if you want to learn a very unique language other than an one people take for career or professional reasons.
Definitely. If you took L1 you know what to expect. Oluseye is great and you learn a lot.
